a'iq], and among them were those who wept, and among them were those who fell unconscious [ghashiya 'alayhi], and among them were those who died in their state of unconsciousness. And Al-Shafi'i, may God have mercy on him, heard a reciter reciting: \"This is a Day on which they will not speak, nor will they be permitted to offer excuses.\" (77:35-36), and he fell unconscious.</div></div></div>"}},"36":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.4","c":"وَلَا","d":"walā","e":"āَlَw"},{"b":"0.56","h":"1.3","c":"يُؤْذَنُ","d":"yu'dhanu","e":"ُnَhdْwʾُy"},{"b":"1.3","h":"2.77","c":"لَهُمْ","d":"lahum","e":"ْmُhَl"},{"b":"1.9","h":"3.68","c":"فَيَعْتَذِرُونَ","d":"fayaʿtadhirūna","e":"َnwُrِhdَtْʿعَyَf"}],"a":{"g":"Nor will it be permitted for them to make an excuse."}},"37":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.7","c":"وَيْلٌ","d":"waylun","e":"ٌlْyَw"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.37","c":"يَوْمَئِذٍ","d":"yawma-idhin","e":"ٍhdِyʾَmْwَy"},{"b":"2.6","h":"4.99","c":"لِلْمُكَذِّبِينَ","d":"lil'mukadhibīna","e":"َnyِbِّhdَkُmْlِّl"}],"a":{"g":"Woe, that Day, to the deniers."}},"38":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.65","c":"هَذَا","d":"hādhā","e":"āَhdَٰh"},{"b":"0.78","h":"2.04","c":"يَوْمُ","d":"yawmu","e":"ُmْwَy"},{"b":"1.4","h":"3.29","c":"الْفَصْلِ","d":"l-faṣli","e":"ِlْṣَfْlٱ"},{"b":"2.2","h":"6.51","c":"جَمَعْنَاكُمْ","d":"jamaʿnākum","e":"ْmُkَٰnْʿعَmَjg"},{"b":"3.6","h":"8.97","c":"وَالْأَوَّلِينَ","d":"wal-awalīna","e":"َnyِlَّwَaʾْlٱَw"}],"a":{"g":"This is the Day of Judgement; We will have assembled you and the former peoples."}},"39":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.03","c":"فَإِنْ","d":"fa-in","e":"nِiʾَf"},{"b":"1.4","h":"1.39","c":"كَانَ","d":"kāna","e":"َnāَk"},{"b":"2.0","h":"2.62","c":"لَكُمْ","d":"lakum","e":"ْmُkَl"},{"b":"2.6","h":"3.63","c":"كَيْدٌ","d":"kaydun","e":"ٌdْyَk"},{"b":"4.2","h":"5.78","c":"فَكِيدُونِ","d":"fakīdūni","e":"ِnwُdyِkَf"}],"a":{"g":"So if you have a plan, then plan against Me."}},"40":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.5","c":"وَيْلٌ","d":"waylun","e":"ٌlْyَw"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.32","c":"يَو